# Asset auto-discovery (mandatory)

**When the operator asks to add, enable, hook up, or ship any asset** or run a batch wave — read [`ASSET_BATCH_EXPANSION_POLICY_V1.md`](../../docs/SOP/ASSET_BATCH_EXPANSION_POLICY_V1.md) for waves.

## First tool pass — before replying

```bash
python scripts/discover_asset_data_source.py --asset <ID> --json
```

Read `next_action` + `agent_steps` from JSON. **Do not ask** which exchange or data vendor.

## Execute in the same session

| `next_action` | Agent does |
|---------------|------------|
| `enable_existing_row` | Witness + `enable_asset_batch.py --apply` + gate + commit |
| `merge_registry_and_enable` | Merge manifest row, witness, enable, PR |
| `switch_venue_and_enable` | Update registry venue, enable, PR |
| `build_adapter` | Implement fetch adapter, then enable |
| `already_enabled` | Report live |
| `blocked_no_live_options` | Document skip; do **not** enable |

Canon: [`ASSET_DATA_SOURCE_DISCOVERY_V1.md`](../../docs/SOP/ASSET_DATA_SOURCE_DISCOVERY_V1.md)
